divs: Sighting DetailsGreat sunny day with no clouds in brooklyn. I took several pics from sunset park because i wanted to make a panoramic picture. Then when i downloaded on my computer and adjusted the contrast, i noticed this kind of disc. Even without correcting the contrast, you can see it. I don't know why there is this on my pic.
